    "description": "Scootsy Holdings Services is actively seeking a talented and motivated Reservation Manager to join our dynamic team in Visakhapatnam. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Scootsy Holdings Services:\nScootsy Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Scootsy Holdings Services!",
